ink?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2F2803301701%2F4567085219583692&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0Eivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=878f6482\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/2803301701/4567085219583692</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T00:35:07.000Z","msg":"點解新彊就新彊建設兵團通報，其他就淨係講省市嘅？"},{"pid":"906e3b092131be14dc11091e70b346434f766c78","tid":2268472,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T00:35:28.000Z","msg":"為病毒打氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ea1564958b7cf184aa6ac92f34a369dc95756f","tid":2268472,"uid":119456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T00:35:47.000Z","msg":"今次輪到邊個發賀電？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfaa3f573710f599cc4d4ad78d48bc232f76db69","tid":2268472,"uid":173817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T00:36:22.000Z","msg":"外星病毒又侵入強國，一定外星人做"},{"pid":"7e4aba953fca0b362d57c8f4caf4f5840596b79f","tid":2268472,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T00:37:33.000Z","msg":"有時覺得 全球最大人體實驗室就係中国入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273a82a2f72c9de07be7d61d97f7f29e2a8d74b9","tid":2268472,"uid":170249,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"79d0b852dece174f30a6772ce1774c13a7fcbf29","tid":2268472,"uid":201398,"like":57,"dislike":3,"score":54,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T00:16:51.000Z","msg":"點解唔計香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T00:37:53.000Z","msg":"有利益咪中國一部份 <br />\n<br />\n冇利益就變港毒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal